definition: to predominate/to occupy a dominant position

sentences.english: “In families, the competitive element is in ascendancy, ” he said.
sentences.chinese: 在家裏，競爭因素是佔優勢的。

sentences.english: Foreign hostility to China’s export dominance is growing.
sentences.chinese: 外國對於中國佔優勢出口的敵意在增加。

sentences.english: The income superiority of the urban natives among unrelated individuals held for both men and women.
sentences.chinese: 原住黑人無論男女，在收入上都佔優勢。

sentences.english: From Zheng cotton high low open view of the situation, short is more dominant.
sentences.chinese: 而從鄭棉高開低走的態勢來看，空頭更佔優勢。

sentences.english: Applying in Arkansas was a big advantage.
sentences.chinese: 在阿肯色州提出申請很佔優勢。

sentences.english: Israel itself has long been superior in weaponry and manpower.
sentences.chinese: 以色列本身一直在武器裝備和人力資源上佔優勢。

sentences.english: The form of ammonium N dominated over the inorganic N in the root-layer soils.
sentences.chinese: 銨態氮在根系層土壤的無機態氮總量中佔優勢。

sentences.english: France was predominant on land, Britain at sea.
sentences.chinese: 法國在陸地上佔優勢，英國則在海上。

sentences.english: At half-time the advantage lay with them.
sentences.chinese: 上半場結束時他們佔優勢。

sentences.english: Tom m's college education gave him an advantage over boys who had not been to a university.
sentences.chinese: 湯姆的大學髧教育使他比沒上過大學的男孩們佔優勢。

sentences.english: They predominate and are of greatest concentration in the central part of the retina.
sentences.chinese: 它們在網膜中部佔優勢，具有最大的濃度。

sentences.english: G. podophylla was the dominant species in the shrub layer.
sentences.chinese: 黑桫欏在灌木層中佔優勢地位。

sentences.english: The higher had more advantages then the latter of reading score at speed-reading strategies;
sentences.chinese: 閱讀成績高分者比低分者在快速閱讀策略上更佔優勢。

sentences.english: An outstanding feature of ancient Chinese is that the monosyllabic words prevail.
sentences.chinese: 古代漢語一個突出特徵是單音詞佔優勢。

sentences.english: But, he pointed out, the dollar is just too dominant for the time being.
sentences.chinese: 他指出，但是美元只是在眼下過於佔優勢。

sentences.english: By the life type analysis, the annual plant gain advantage.
sentences.chinese: 生活型分析表明一年生植物佔優勢。
